        },
        "16371346550ab9a1d7-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Howard’s Folly is an inspiring blend of three key ingredients: an <em>innovative</em> partnership between Chief Winemaker, David Baverstock, and entrepreneur, Howard Bilton; their joint <em>passion</em> to unlock the best of Portugal’s grape varietals; and, a <em>mission</em> to give something back through sponsorship of an arts-based charity for underprivileged children, the Sovereign Art Foundation.</p><p><em>Innovation</em>, <em>passion</em> and <em>mission</em> drive everything we do, resulting in consistent production of delicious award-winning wines.</p>"
